    <div class="tip">
      <h2>1. Try the 4-7-8 Breathing Technique</h2>
      <p>Inhale for 4 seconds, hold for 7, exhale for 8. Repeat for 3-4 rounds to calm your nervous system fast.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="tip">
      <h2>2. Use a Guided Meditation App</h2>
      <p>Apps like <a href="https://www.calm.com/" target="_blank">Calm</a> or <a href="https://www.headspace.com/" target="_blank">Headspace</a> offer short meditations for stress relief.</p>
    </div>

